  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2181568/" class="title-link">看书的疑问</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2181568"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/flyine-seasky/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4459224-14.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/flyine-seasky/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">海天</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-07-31"
      class="main-meta">2009-07-31 08:49:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2181568_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在191页第三段第三句话“他（指的是秦始皇）把剩余的地区分为省和区，中央政府直接听命于皇帝……”中，很明显，秦朝时实施的是郡县制，而在文献翻译中，郡县二字可能被翻译成了province以及district或者region。那么在回译的时候就不能直接译为”郡“和”县“么？

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2181568/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 0没用</span>
